generated_cypher: MATCH (p:Person)-[:DIRECTED]->(m:Movie) WHERE m.votes > 1000 RETURN p.name AS Director, m.title AS Movie, m.votes AS Votes ORDER BY m.votes DESC LIMIT 50;

question: What are the top 5 reviewed movies by summary 'An amazing journey'?

question: Who are the first three actors born after 1970 who acted in a movie released before 1990?

question: How many people born before 1950 have directed a movie?
generated_cypher: MATCH (p:Person)-[:DIRECTED]->(m:Movie) WHERE p.born < 1950 RETURN COUNT(p) AS DirectorsCount LIMIT 1;
generated_result: [{"DirectorsCount": 17}]

question: What is the highest rating given to any movie by any person?

question: List the movies with the summary "A solid romp".
generated_cypher: MATCH (m:Movie) WHERE m.tagline = "A solid romp" RETURN m.title AS Movie, m.released AS Released, m.votes AS Votes ORDER BY m.title LIMIT 50;

question: What is the average number of votes for movies released in the same year as "The Matrix Revolutions"?
generated_cypher: MATCH (m:Movie {title: "The Matrix Revolutions"}) WITH m.released AS release_year MATCH (m2:Movie) WHERE m2.released = release_year RETURN AVG(m2.votes) AS AverageVotes LIMIT 1;
generated_result: [{"AverageVotes": 1180.0}]
